MyBroadband is South Africa’s most powerful IT publication with 3 million monthly readers – the country’s largest IT and telecoms community. What sets MyBroadband apart from other publications is its exceptional reach into the B2B and B2C markets. Most MyBroadband visitors are IT decision-makers who advise their companies and friends on which products and services to buy. MyBroadband is particularly popular among CEOs, business owners, and IT managers who want the latest news about the local IT market. Here is a breakdown of MyBroadband’s audience in February 2022. MyBroadband is the first publication many IT executives open in the morning and the last one they close before going to bed. It is the window to the South African IT market, which is why top IT companies partner with MyBroadband to ensure their message gets to the local IT community. MyBroadband, therefore, provides ICT companies with a single place to reach the most influential IT decision-makers in South Africa.